{"word":"G2370 - θυμιάω - thymiáō - thoo-mee-ah'-o - Burn incense","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θυμιάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">thymiáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">thoo-mee-ah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Burn incense</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தூபங்காட்டு"},{"paragraph":"to burn incense"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a derivative of <a href=\"#/G2380 - θύω - thýō - thoo'-o/2380\">G2380</a> (in the sense of <i>smoking</i>); to <i>fumigate</i>, that is, <i>offer</i> aromatic <i>fumes:</i> - burn incense.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}